  <tr>
    <td>
      Hi there,<br />
      <br />
      Things has been updated with support for macOS Sonoma, iOS 17, and
      watchOS 10. The update also includes a variety of <b>great improvements for widgets</b>.
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<table>
  <tr>
